Nollywood comic actor, John Okafor, aka Mr. Ibu is said to have been hit by stroke. Reports say the actor has been down for a while, and has asked Nigerians to pray for him at this period. The sickness was said to have started shortly after the 57-year old actor returned from a trip to Owerri. Actors Guild of Nigeria’s President, Emeka Rollas, however, said that the Enugu State-born actor is fast recovering. Details shortly…